STATE
v.
Milton E. LANCASTER. No. 161P07-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 24, 2008. Joan M. Cunningham, Assistant Attorney General, Scott Thomas, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 10th day of January 2008 by Defendant for "Notice of Appeal":
